"uid":140872,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"請問慘爪步槍II最高果舊野打咩出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/01/211546_cc92df2f8ca5e0ce22093b2f4b394007.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F01%2F211546_cc92df2f8ca5e0ce22093b2f4b394007.jpeg&h=b0a59135&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b47ef1801a6bead08b5b501c4c847e285c93a98a","tid":547474,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:16:20.000Z","msg":"笛個高週波有咩用"},{"pid":"282d3f9a2bf8e6b3a3b97f3240dd7f20c78c38bc","tid":547474,"uid":51804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"想問下玩蟲棍既巴打用開咩蟲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n斬擊/打擊？<br />\n力量/速度/體力？<br />\n特化/平衡？<br />\n<br />\n利申 前幾代都係用太刀同雙刀,<br />\n今集手痕想試下新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外仲想問下有咩上位裝推薦岩蟲棍用, 唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98f3ed657e42b4d78a9664302845b8ab066315b","tid":547474,"uid":91132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:19:54.000Z","msg":"今日入坑，歡迎加好友一齊玩<br />\npsn id : ericyuen45<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99285909459f01e114cd9bb6daf34f71de5b32e5","tid":547474,"uid":146180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:27:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以話我知滅盡龍大劍 升到最高要咩材料？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256c6c5a9ca980604c0db0720f2cc4b0235fe83a","tid":547474,"uid":159136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"juno招飛龍在天點避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f23e0af35cec378e3c4cebd0b5f576e99de28a1","tid":547474,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"自由任熔山龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/01/215757_e79357e8b677bce5561c0c0e63042d2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F01%2F215757_e79357e8b677bce5561c0c0e63042d2e.png&h=1206a539&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65a4becfdeb2433c499db6801af5be85ea3d1a45","tid":547474,"uid":72698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"256c6c5a9ca980604c0db0720f2cc4b0235fe83a","tid":547474,"uid":159136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"juno招飛龍在天點避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:58:12.000Z","msg":"飛落黎過下緊急迴避"},{"pid":"f1e22c18d8c0230277bba374b1167470c18e7fcd","tid":547474,"uid":72698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>juno招飛龍在天點避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>飛落黎個下緊急迴避</blockquote>"},{"pid":"337be255748d6d2ccd3f563a9e57c61b0c88306b","tid":547474,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f23e0af35cec378e3c4cebd0b5f576e99de28a1","tid":547474,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"自由任熔山龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/01/215757_e79357e8b677bce5561c0c0e63042d2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F01%2F215757_e79357e8b677bce5561c0c0e63042d2e.png&h=1206a539&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}